graph TD
    A[Local 'launch_job.py'] -->|Configures| B[PyTorch Estimator]
    B -->|Calls .fit()| C{SageMaker Training Infrastructure}
    
    subgraph Asynchronous Cloud Execution
    C --> D[Uploads 'train.py' to S3]
    C --> E[Provisions EC2 Instances]
    C --> F[Downloads S3 Data to instances]
    D & E & F --> G[Executes 'train.py' with Hyperparameters]
    G -->|Outputs model.pth| H[Saves Artifact to S3]
    end
    
    A -.->|Waits for logs| C
    G -.->|Streams metrics| A
